    <!-- Application Structure Plan:
        1. Hero Section: Sets the tone (Old Roman) and introduces the group's purpose (Marketing/Tourism Network).
        2. The Triumvirate of Metrics (Dashboard): Visualizes 'Why Join' using Chart.js (Network Growth, Skill Acquisition).
        3. The XII Tables (Rules): Interactive cards that expand to explain the specific Meta rules and group decrees (No AI Spam, etc.).
        4. The Sunday Games (Schedule): A visual timeline/bar chart showing the focus on Sunday Viral Content sharing.
        5. Enlistment (Interactive Form): A mock "quiz" for the 3 entry questions to prepare users for the real Facebook join request.
    -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices:
        1. Radar Chart: To show "Ideal Gladiator Attributes" (Creativity, Strategy, etc.) - Goal: Inform users of value.
        2. Line Chart: To project "Network Expansion" over time - Goal: Motivate users to join.
        3. Interactive Cards: For Rules - Goal: Organize information cleanly without walls of text.
        4. No SVG/Mermaid used. All icons are unicode or CSS shapes. Charts are Canvas.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
